Insight (Positive)

Positive Insight

KPI

Average First Response Hours and Average Days Open

Good or Bad

Good

Responsible Dim

Work Shifts

What is good

Either First Response Hours or Average Days Open are above average

Where it occurred

In Plano, TX

When it occurred

08/03/2020-08/11/2020

The Extent of the good

only work shift from 11am to 3pm is showing lower Average First Response hours and Days Open (which is red color)

How I know it is good

Three of the work shifts have 0.00 Average days open and the Average First Response hours for 7pm-7am is 16.64, 7am-11am is 15.71 and 3pm-7pm is 10.58 which is lower than the goal (24).
